Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.23,0:21:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐快看 是流星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.09,0:21:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 有那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.69,0:21:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你许愿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:21:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
